<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821828>
    dc:description "FIGURE 812. Polynema pratensiphagum Walley, habitus. Canada, Ontario, London, emerged 5.vi.2000, in lab. J. Whistlecraft, ex. Lygus lineolaris eggs placed in alfalfa block 2.vi.2000. Scale bar=500 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821828/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821838>
    dc:description "FIGURE 827. Polynema (Doriclytus) sp., habitus. Canada, Ontario, Malborough Forest, 45°05'42\"N 75°50'42\"W, 26.vi.2002, H. Goulet & C. Boudreault, maple/beech forest. Scale bar=500 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821838/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821840>
    dc:description "FIGURES 828–833. Polynema sp. (subgenus uncertain unless specified), head. 828, Polynema (Doriclytus) sp., anterior; 829, posterior; 830, lateral; 831, Polynema (Doriclytus) sp., dorsal; 832, Polynema (Polynema) sp., ventral; 833, mouthparts. Scale bars: 828–832=50 μm; 833=100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821840/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821830>
    dc:description "FIGURES 813–817. Polynema (Polynema) sp., head except 817. 813, anterior; 814, posterior; 815a, lateral; 815b, lateral (internal) showing ocular apodeme; 816, dorsal; 817, antenna. Scale bars: 813–816=100 μm; 817=200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821830/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821836>
    dc:description "FIGURES 824–826. Polynema (Polynema) sp., male. 824, metasoma, lateral; 825, genitalia seen through gaster; 826, wings. Scale bars: 824, 825=100 μm; 826=500 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821836/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821842>
    dc:description "FIGURES 834–841. Polynema sp. (subgenus uncertain unless specified), mesosoma except 840 and 841. 834, dorsal; 835, lateral; 836, Polynema (Doriclytus) sp., ventral; 837, Polynema (Polynema) sp., ventral; 838, Polynema (Polynema) sp., anterior; 839, frenum–propodeum; 840, petiole, lateral; 841, petiole, ventral. Scale bars: 834–839=50 μm; 840, 841=20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821842/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821832>
    dc:description "FIGURES 818–820. Polynema (Polynema) sp., mesosoma. 818, dorsal; 819, lateral; 820, including petiole, ventral. Scale bars=200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821832/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821804>
    dc:description "FIGURES 760–768. Palaeoneura sophoniae (Huber). 760, mesosoma, dorsal; 761, mesosoma, lateral; 762, mesosoma, ventral, with coxae; 763, mesosoma ventral, without coxae; 764, mesosoma, anterior; 765, mesosoma, posterior; 766, petiole, dorsal; 767, petiole, lateral; 768, petiole, ventral. Scale bars: 760–765=50 μm; 766–768=20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821804/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821814>
    dc:description "FIGURES 784–788. Palaeoneura mymaripennis (Dozier), mesosoma. 784, dorsal; 785, lateral; 786, ventral; 787, male, anterior; 788, scutellum–propodeum. Scale bars=50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821814/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821802>
    dc:description "FIGURES 754–759. Palaeoneura sophoniae (Huber), head. 754, anterior; 755, posterior; 756, lateral; 757, dorsal; 758, ventral; 759, mouthparts. Scale bars=20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821802/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3821812>
    dc:description "FIGURES 778–783. Palaeoneura mymaripennis (Dozier), head. 778, anterior; 779, posterior; 780, lateral; 781, dorsal; 782, male, ventral; 783, male mouthparts. Scale bars=50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3821812/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

